1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 24=

3
00:00:32,812 --> 00:00:33,613
Liu San!

4
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:34,840
Surrender now!

5
00:00:46,679 --> 00:00:48,359
Yu, you're finally here.

6
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:49,600
Wushuang?

7
00:00:49,700 --> 00:00:50,679
What are you doing here?

8
00:00:53,550 --> 00:00:56,825
(Meditation Hall)

9
00:01:15,437 --> 00:01:16,596
Are you Liu San the thief?

10
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:21,840
The Sect Leader of the Sacred Hand Sect
pays me a visit.

11
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:24,760
I'm honored indeed.

12
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:26,280
Since you know who I am,

13
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,439
then get out of the Capital now.

14
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:32,000
Otherwise,
as Grandmaster of the Martial Alliance,

15
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,359
I'll deal with you accordingly.

16
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:38,040
What?

17
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:42,280
Are you going to issue a kill order
to the entire Martial Alliance?

18
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:44,040
Try me if you don't believe it.

19
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:46,439
Are you truly the Grandmaster?

20
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,079
In that case,

21
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:51,120
you must be the Jade Squirrel as well.

22
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,879
Does whether I'm the Jade Squirrel

23
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,760
matter to you?

24
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,760
Naturally.

25
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:01,400
If you really are the Jade Squirrel,

26
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,840
I'll stop my villainy.

27
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:08,879
Where's the Sacred Token?

28
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:09,960
Let me see it.

29
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:13,520
Why do I feel like this is a ruse?

30
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:17,240
If that's the case,

31
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:20,039
you're asking for death.

32
00:02:21,832 --> 00:02:22,832
You're using empty words

33
00:02:22,832 --> 00:02:24,912
to claim you're the Sect Leader
and the Grandmaster.

34
00:02:24,912 --> 00:02:25,993
How can I believe you?

35
00:02:26,649 --> 00:02:27,450
If you truly are

36
00:02:27,450 --> 00:02:29,250
the Sect Leader and the Jade Squirrel,

37
00:02:29,512 --> 00:02:30,633
then I shall

38
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:33,080
pack up and head back to Xichuan,

39
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,080
never to show my face again.

40
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:36,159
Otherwise,

41
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,240
why should I listen to you?

42
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,719
You're playing me!

43
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,560
What?

44
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,990
We've been talking a lot.

45
00:03:08,439 --> 00:03:09,439
I'm now hungry.

46
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:14,500
Liu San, are you indeed

47
00:03:15,912 --> 00:03:17,352
a weird one.

48
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:19,120
Enough talk.

49
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:21,879
I suggest you confess today,

50
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:24,800
or don't blame me for what follows.

51
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,039
It's all a trap!

52
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:26,680
Sister!

53
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:29,599
Sister!

54
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:34,159
Let me go!

55
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:36,360
This is a trap!

56
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,800
Luo Wushuang set this up!

57
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:46,319
Guys,

58
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,639
did you all hear that?

59
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,639
Luo Wushuang?

60
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,599
It's you!

61
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:02,319
You're the bandit, Liu San?

62
00:04:03,719 --> 00:04:04,879
What bandit?

63
00:04:05,543 --> 00:04:06,462
This is Deputy Su Peng,

64
00:04:06,462 --> 00:04:09,462
whom I've brought
all the way from Xichuan.

65
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,719
I've asked for your help

66
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:14,280
specifically for this matter.

67
00:04:16,242 --> 00:04:16,962
In the past,

68
00:04:16,962 --> 00:04:19,402
my attempts to expose
Yunchang's identity failed

69
00:04:19,525 --> 00:04:20,525
because

70
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:23,199
she had too many people protecting her.

71
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:25,199
As you said,

72
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:27,560
to take down this Grandmaster,

73
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:30,439
we had to isolate her
from her inner circle.

74
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:33,600
Once we found her weakness,

75
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:35,319
we could lure her out.

76
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,879
She has a simple-minded maid

77
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:39,560
named Zhizhi.

78
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:42,120
She is a simpleton
and an infatuated girl.

79
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:44,120
She is the key.

80
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:46,199
I'll win her over,

81
00:04:46,287 --> 00:04:47,287
make her fall for me,

82
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:49,439
and she'll tell us every secret

83
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:50,680
Chu Yunchang's been hiding.

84
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:52,560
Once we've dealt with Liu San,

85
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,519
we'll go back to your hometown

86
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:55,680
and be together forever.

87
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:02,279
With a simple ruse,

88
00:05:02,659 --> 00:05:04,300
he's played both of you fools

89
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:05,539
like a fiddle.

90
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,800
Chu Yunchang.

91
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,519
Surrender now.

92
00:05:09,519 --> 00:05:10,800
It's all my fault.

93
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:14,120
To get to me,

94
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,160
you toyed with Zhizhi's heart?

95
00:05:16,759 --> 00:05:18,399
She brought this on herself.

96
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,800
Where's Liu Jun?

97
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:22,959
I want to see him.

98
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,199
He helped me capture you.

99
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,439
He's done a great service.

100
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,639
By now,

101
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:30,519
it's likely my grandfather
has promoted him to Chief Constable.

102
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:32,240
He's already on his way back to Xichuan.

103
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:35,040
You poor, foolish girl.

104
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:38,439
You really thought
you'd found true love.

105
00:05:38,959 --> 00:05:40,800
Look at yourself.

106
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,519
What man could ever truly love you?

107
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,680
Utterly despicable!

108
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:47,439
Luo Wushuang.

109
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,920
You've hurt so many people

110
00:05:49,162 --> 00:05:50,601
just to catch me.

111
00:05:51,087 --> 00:05:52,327
The merchants who were robbed

112
00:05:52,675 --> 00:05:53,770
and the injured constables

113
00:05:53,959 --> 00:05:55,279
have done nothing wrong!

114
00:05:55,487 --> 00:05:56,368
First of all,

115
00:05:56,787 --> 00:05:59,547
the merchants' money has
already been returned in full.

116
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:03,279
Su Peng only caused injuries.
He took no lives.

117
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,120
As for those constables,

118
00:06:05,439 --> 00:06:07,120
they are men of the law.

119
00:06:07,279 --> 00:06:09,680
Getting hurt in the line of duty
is unavoidable.

120
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,279
Besides,

121
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:14,720
Commissioner Luo will
reward them for their merit.

122
00:06:15,279 --> 00:06:16,439
Have you no conscience?

123
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:18,639
It's only because you're so difficult,
Chu Yunchang.

124
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,839
So, to capture you,

125
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,360
making a few small sacrifices

126
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,680
is perfectly normal.

127
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,759
Chu Yunchang.

128
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:28,000
If you'd only confessed sooner,

129
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:30,759
none of this would've happened.

130
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:33,360
Luo Wushuang,

131
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:37,399
I never thought
a constable could be so low.

132
00:06:37,399 --> 00:06:38,439
You're calling me low?

133
00:06:39,878 --> 00:06:41,387
A lowly thief is calling

134
00:06:41,387 --> 00:06:43,117
the thief catchers low?

135
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,000
We may be people of the Martial World,

136
00:06:45,550 --> 00:06:47,831
but we've never done anything
to harm the innocent.

137
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,000
My aunt and her husband
gave everything they stole

138
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,759
to the poor.

139
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,600
And you?

140
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:55,519
You talk about honor and morality,

141
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:58,279
yet you've resorted to dirty tactics.

142
00:06:58,959 --> 00:07:00,279
You dare speak of being dirty?

143
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:03,160
You've spent your life hiding,

144
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:05,480
too afraid to admit
you're the Jade Squirrel.

145
00:07:05,959 --> 00:07:06,839
Chu Yunchang.

146
00:07:07,262 --> 00:07:08,622
You stand here before me,

147
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,920
sounding so righteous.

148
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,399
But tell me,

149
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:15,920
would you dare repeat that to Mao Buyu?

150
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,600
You...

151
00:07:49,812 --> 00:07:55,837
♪My heart's desire is tangled
by the chaos of this world♪

152
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:58,680
Why?

153
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,399
I didn't mean to deceive you.

154
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,600
Why did you come?

155
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:09,120
Buyu, you knew this whole time?

156
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,720
Do you both take me for a fool?

157
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:16,000
You've been putting on a show for us.

158
00:08:18,762 --> 00:08:19,841
Do you have any idea

159
00:08:19,841 --> 00:08:21,362
how much I've struggled lately?

160
00:08:21,362 --> 00:08:24,325
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

161
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,120
Chang.

162
00:08:26,879 --> 00:08:27,920
The wound on your hand

163
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,800
is the same as the Jade Squirrel's.

164
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,039
(What if)

165
00:08:33,399 --> 00:08:35,480
I really were the Jade Squirrel,

166
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,360
what would you do?

167
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:38,919
Chang.

168
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,200
(My answer is the same.)

169
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:41,679
(A thief is a thief,)

170
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,000
(and I'm an officer.)

171
00:08:43,639 --> 00:08:45,600
It's my duty to catch thieves.

172
00:08:45,650 --> 00:08:47,700
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

173
00:08:47,762 --> 00:08:51,250
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

174
00:08:51,799 --> 00:08:52,720
(I don't want lies)

175
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,000
(between us.)

176
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,679
(Even the deepest bond)

177
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:57,519
(can't withstand constant deception.)

178
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,559
(Do you understand?)

179
00:09:01,137 --> 00:09:04,962
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

180
00:09:05,012 --> 00:09:09,862
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

181
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:10,519
Don't run!

182
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,639
I'm a constable.

183
00:09:19,937 --> 00:09:21,538
Catching criminals is my calling.

184
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,759
But I truly didn't want to expose you.

185
00:09:26,279 --> 00:09:27,120
Every single day,

186
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,440
I hoped we'd be married soon.

187
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:31,639
You swore that you'd be a devoted wife,

188
00:09:31,639 --> 00:09:33,680
and never be involved
in the Martial World again.

189
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,600
So why did you have to show up tonight?

190
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:41,639
I wanted to resolve
this as quickly as possible,

191
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:46,600
so nothing would stand
in the way of our wedding.

192
00:09:46,662 --> 00:09:50,500
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

193
00:09:50,519 --> 00:09:51,960
You don't trust me at all.

194
00:09:53,220 --> 00:09:54,919
You've been lying to me
this entire time.

195
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:57,080
What about you?

196
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,480
Haven't you been lying to me?

197
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,320
I haven't!

198
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:05,840
I've been playing the fool.

199
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:08,879
I did everything I could

200
00:10:08,879 --> 00:10:10,519
to prove that I was wrong about you.

201
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:12,519
But look where we are.

202
00:10:14,399 --> 00:10:15,440
My biggest mistake

203
00:10:16,700 --> 00:10:17,890
was falling in love with you,

204
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,039
trusting you,

205
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:21,960
and indulging you!

206
00:10:22,987 --> 00:10:27,237
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

207
00:10:27,337 --> 00:10:30,400
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

208
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:33,120
I truly love you.

209
00:10:33,362 --> 00:10:35,812
♪The moon traces your face♪

210
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,159
But I'm so exhausted.

211
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,200
I've been lying to you.

212
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:43,759
But I really...

213
00:10:45,759 --> 00:10:47,679
I really wanted to grow old with you.

214
00:10:50,159 --> 00:10:51,000
I thought

215
00:10:53,279 --> 00:10:55,159
I could keep up the lie for a lifetime.

216
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,759
But in the end,

217
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:03,559
I realized

218
00:11:03,799 --> 00:11:06,240
that I was slowly losing myself.

219
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,960
Enough, both of you!

220
00:11:15,519 --> 00:11:16,320
Mao Buyu.

221
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,159
You are harboring a criminal.

222
00:11:18,399 --> 00:11:19,720
I will deal with you later.

223
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,320
Chu Yunchang.

224
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,879
I am placing you under arrest.

225
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:25,720
I'd like to see you try.

226
00:11:26,879 --> 00:11:27,639
Seize her!

227
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:32,679
If you resist arrest,

228
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,200
she'll be the first to die.

229
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:39,679
Mao Buyu.

230
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:42,279
We have the witness and the evidence.

231
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:43,480
I'm taking her in.

232
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,200
Any objection?

233
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,840
That's more like it.

234
00:11:59,279 --> 00:12:01,000
People like the Jade Squirrel

235
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:02,679
belong behind bars.

236
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:03,799
Take her away!

237
00:12:03,799 --> 00:12:04,399
Understood!

238
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:05,799
Buyu...

239
00:12:24,679 --> 00:12:25,320
Yu.

240
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,159
What are you doing?

241
00:12:28,639 --> 00:12:29,279
Wushuang.

242
00:12:30,279 --> 00:12:31,679
When did you become so ruthless

243
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:34,320
just to get what you want?

244
00:12:35,679 --> 00:12:37,360
Which one of us really changed?

245
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:40,120
I'm just doing my job.

246
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:40,879
What about you?

247
00:12:42,519 --> 00:12:44,519
A constable's job is to stop crime

248
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,759
and protect the people.

249
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:47,480
The Sacred Hand Sect is a cancer

250
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,399
on this city.

251
00:12:48,399 --> 00:12:50,559
But what have they actually done wrong?

252
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:53,279
The people have nothing
but praise for them.

253
00:12:53,759 --> 00:12:55,519
That's exactly why they're dangerous.

254
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,279
They're a rogue sect

255
00:12:57,279 --> 00:12:59,200
trying to write their own laws.

256
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:01,879
They help the poor just to buy loyalty.

257
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,480
It's a conspiracy.

258
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,720
If the people only answer to them,

259
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,519
where does that leave our authority?

260
00:13:07,679 --> 00:13:09,240
The law would mean nothing.

261
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:11,759
Mao Buyu.

262
00:13:13,260 --> 00:13:14,960
Don't come to work
for the next few days.

263
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,679
Stay home and reflect on it.

264
00:13:28,519 --> 00:13:29,159
Sister.

265
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:31,240
It's all my fault.

266
00:13:31,679 --> 00:13:33,720
Please don't be mad at me.

267
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:36,000
I don't blame you.

268
00:13:36,559 --> 00:13:37,679
Stop crying, alright?

269
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:48,840
Who goes there?

270
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,120
We're escorting the prisoner.

271
00:13:50,510 --> 00:13:51,537
Deputy Wushuang's orders.

272
00:13:51,537 --> 00:13:52,777
She'll be escorting her.

273
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:53,960
No need to trouble her.

274
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,000
Commissioner Luo's orders.

275
00:13:55,412 --> 00:13:57,637
We're taking the prisoner
exactly where she belongs.

276
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:58,559
What?

277
00:13:58,919 --> 00:14:00,000
Stop arguing.

278
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:00,759
Move aside.

279
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:02,840
Move.

280
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:12,975
(Buddha)

281
00:14:15,012 --> 00:14:15,813
Hold it right there!

282
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:17,880
Let me see the transfer order!

283
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,799
Something feels off about this route.

284
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:31,960
This is not right.

285
00:14:37,639 --> 00:14:39,080
Where exactly are you taking me?

286
00:14:40,159 --> 00:14:41,279
Who are you people?

287
00:14:44,650 --> 00:14:46,850
(Big Buddha Temple)

288
00:14:51,919 --> 00:14:52,799
Deputy Luo.

289
00:14:53,900 --> 00:14:55,200
I told you to guard the prisoner.

290
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,080
Why are you back?

291
00:14:56,639 --> 00:14:57,480
Where is she?

292
00:14:57,679 --> 00:14:59,919
The two men at the wagon
said they had orders

293
00:15:00,039 --> 00:15:01,240
from Commissioner Luo.

294
00:15:01,399 --> 00:15:03,240
They have already
taken the prisoner ahead.

295
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:04,271
Nonsense!

296
00:15:04,437 --> 00:15:05,691
My grandfather put me

297
00:15:05,691 --> 00:15:06,650
in charge of this case.

298
00:15:06,650 --> 00:15:08,250
Why would he suddenly send someone else?

299
00:15:08,977 --> 00:15:09,737
You useless fools!

300
00:15:09,737 --> 00:15:10,578
Go after them now!

301
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:11,679
Bring them back,

302
00:15:11,679 --> 00:15:13,159
or I will have you all flogged!

303
00:15:13,559 --> 00:15:14,159
Yes!

304
00:15:24,279 --> 00:15:25,360
What are you doing?

305
00:15:27,039 --> 00:15:28,120
Auntie! Squire Mei!

306
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:30,919
It is us, Chang.

307
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:32,559
How did you find me?

308
00:15:38,159 --> 00:15:38,879
Who was that?

309
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:47,720
That Mao Buyu

310
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,000
is far too pedantic.

311
00:15:49,445 --> 00:15:52,085
Even a spoiled brat like Luo Wuxia
is more reliable than him.

312
00:15:52,475 --> 00:15:54,034
Thank you for saving me.

313
00:15:54,799 --> 00:15:56,480
But we can't stay here and talk.

314
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,770
Let's find somewhere safe first.

315
00:15:57,801 --> 00:15:58,562
Go on ahead.

316
00:15:58,562 --> 00:16:00,390
I'll leave a few false tracks
for our pursuers.

317
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:02,320
Go on.

318
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,080
Come on.

319
00:16:10,559 --> 00:16:11,639
It's all my fault.

320
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,240
I'm the one to blame.

321
00:16:15,759 --> 00:16:17,440
I shouldn't have ignored your advice.

322
00:16:18,399 --> 00:16:19,639
I was stubborn and petty.

323
00:16:20,639 --> 00:16:23,240
I was so blind
to fall for a monster like him.

324
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:26,360
I didn't just ruin my own life,

325
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:29,559
I've hurt every single one of you.

326
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,639
Come on, get up.

327
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:33,799
Madam.

328
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:36,720
Even if you killed me right now,

329
00:16:37,799 --> 00:16:39,519
I'd have no right to complain.

330
00:16:42,559 --> 00:16:44,000
How could I ever blame you?

331
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,320
It wasn't your fault.

332
00:16:48,759 --> 00:16:49,559
No...

333
00:16:53,759 --> 00:16:54,679
Get up.

334
00:16:56,399 --> 00:16:57,080
Get up.

335
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,200
You silly girl.

336
00:17:01,210 --> 00:17:02,600
How can you possibly blame yourself?

337
00:17:02,679 --> 00:17:04,480
If loving someone is a mistake,

338
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:06,680
then no one in this world
is ever in the right.

339
00:17:07,799 --> 00:17:08,480
Stop crying.

340
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,400
I've put you all in danger.

341
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:13,960
But most of all,

342
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:16,279
I've put Yunchang in danger.

343
00:17:18,759 --> 00:17:19,519
Actually,

344
00:17:22,079 --> 00:17:24,279
I feel a strange sense of relief.

345
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,600
Buyu and I can finally

346
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:31,720
stop living a lie.

347
00:17:37,050 --> 00:17:40,325
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

348
00:17:40,363 --> 00:17:43,238
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

349
00:17:43,738 --> 00:17:49,456
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

350
00:17:50,638 --> 00:17:53,958
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

351
00:17:54,088 --> 00:17:57,008
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

352
00:17:58,176 --> 00:18:03,416
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

353
00:18:04,638 --> 00:18:07,031
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

354
00:18:07,031 --> 00:18:10,681
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

355
00:18:10,750 --> 00:18:14,240
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

356
00:18:14,338 --> 00:18:17,313
♪To the ends of time♪

357
00:18:17,313 --> 00:18:20,688
♪The moon traces your face♪

358
00:18:20,875 --> 00:18:24,463
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

359
00:18:24,463 --> 00:18:30,703
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

360
00:18:31,038 --> 00:18:34,253
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

361
00:18:34,538 --> 00:18:38,076
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

362
00:18:38,363 --> 00:18:41,388
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

363
00:18:41,388 --> 00:18:44,488
♪On our way to forever♪

364
00:18:44,488 --> 00:18:48,338
♪The moon traces your face♪

365
00:18:48,338 --> 00:18:51,698
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

366
00:18:51,888 --> 00:18:57,848
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

367
00:18:58,925 --> 00:19:08,565
♪Just to be with you♪
